text.section:
In addition to fees created by KRS 23A.205, 23A.206, and 23A.2065, an administrative fee of thirty dollars ($30) shall be added to the costs that the defendant is required to pay for the following crimes:
A sex crime, meaning an offense described in:
KRS Chapter 510;
KRS 530.020;
KRS 530.064(1)(a);
KRS 531.310; and
KRS 531.320;
Stalking, meaning conduct prohibited under KRS 508.140 and 508.150; and
A criminal attempt, conspiracy, facilitation, or solicitation to commit the crimes set forth in this subsection.
